    "url": "http://localhost:4000/sta-blog//introducing-sto-listing-by-security-token-club/",
    "title": "Introducing STO listing by Security Token Club",
    "body": "2018/12/28 - This August, we created our first Security Token Club Telegram channel. Fast forward to five months later, Security Token Club is present in five regions (International, Russia, Japan, Korea, Turkey), with over 900 participants worldwide and multiple events organized in Russia, Singapore and Hong Kong. A couple of days ago, a 400th member joined Security Token Club Russia Telegram group, our biggest local community by far. As a New Year gift and a thank you for our friends and followers, Evercity &amp; Security Token Club are happy to announce the first release of Security Token Listing*, compiled by our team upon numerous requests. You are welcome to comment, discuss and suggest changes‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääjoin us at https://t. me/stoaccelerator ! If you are planning a security token offering for your company‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääe-mail us at sto@evercity. io for details. ‚Äî *The listing is created for informational purposes only and does not constitute an investment advice. "
